This code requires haskell-rpm which is a separate git repo, but is also
a subtree in this git repo.  So you don't really need to go get it separately.

RUNNING LOCALLY
===============

$ cabal sandbox init
$ cabal install --dependencies-only
$ cabal build
$ cabal run import -- metadata.db Packages/*rpm


RUNNING DOCKERLY
================

$ cd ..
$ sudo docker build -t bdcs .
$ sudo docker run -v /home/clumens/mddb:/mddb -v /home/clumens/Packages:/rpms:ro --rm -it bdcs
